{{1999–2000 Big East men's basketball standings}}
The '''1999&ndash;2000 St. John's Red Storm men's basketball team''' represented [[St. John's University (New York)|St. John's University]] during the [[1999–00 NCAA Division I men's basketball season]]. The team was coached by [[Mike Jarvis]] in his second year at the school. St. John's home games are played at [[Carnesecca Arena|Alumni Hall]] and [[Madison Square Garden]] and the team is a member of the [[Big East Conference (1979–2013)|Big East Conference]].

